---
// Honors Student component with logo and text section
---

<section id="honors-student" class="honors-student">
	<div class="honors-container">
		<!-- Text Section -->
		<div class="text-section">
			<h2 class="section-title">Honors Student</h2>
			<p>
                The Honors Program is a competitive academic program that offers high-achieving students the opportunity to engage in advanced coursework, research, and community service.
            </p>
            <p>
                As an honors student at Central Michigan University, I have taken unexpected classes, like ASL and the Virtues of the Korean Independence Movement.
            </p>
            <p>
                I studied abroad in Athens, Greece, for four months and embraced the chance to learn about different cultures and perspectives. 
            </p>
            <p>
                I conducted a capston project, combining my interest in UX and coding to develop a desktop application that helps CMU students complete homework for networking and computer science classes. 
            </p>
            <br>
            <p >
                 <a  class="button-primary" href="/projects/Labs@Home">Learn more about my capstone, Labs@Home!</a>
            </p>
		</div>

		<!-- Logo Section -->
		<div class="logo-section">
			<img src="/hon/logo.png" alt="Honors Student Logo" class="honors-logo" />
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.honors-student {
		padding: 80px 20px;
		background-color: #ffffff;
		font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
	}

	.honors-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 60px;
		align-items: center;
	}

	/* Text Section */
	.text-section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: flex-start;
	}

	.text-section .section-title {
		font-size: 2.5em;
		margin: 0 0 20px 0;
		color: #1f2937;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.text-section p {
		font-size: 1.05em;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #4b5563;
		margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
	}

    .capstone-link{
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

	.capstone-link:hover {
		color: var(--color-secondary);
	}


	/* Logo Section */
	.logo-section {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.honors-logo {
		max-width: 75%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: white;
		padding: 20px;
	}

	/* Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.honors-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 30px;
		}

		.text-section .section-title {
			font-size: 1.8em;
		}

		.honors-logo {
			max-width: 300px;
		}
	}
</style>
